{"id":587742,"link":"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2018/06/【cdtv】last-week-tonight-with-john-oliver习近平特别版（中文字幕）/","date":"2018-06-27T01:22:06Z","modified":"2018-06-27T01:26:49Z","title":"【CDTV】《约翰奥利佛上周今夜秀》习近平特别版（中字）","content":"<p>6月17日，英国著名脱口秀主持人约翰·奥利佛（John Oliver）在他的每周节目《上周今夜秀》（Last Week Tonight）中批评了中国国家主席习近平，节目时长达20min。（BBC）</p>\n<p>6月18日，中国数字时代转发了该节目末尾一首改编的歌曲<a href=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2018/06/%E3%80%90%E4%BC%97%E4%BA%BA%E6%8E%A8%E3%80%91%E3%80%8Athis-is-the-china-xi%E3%80%8B/\">《This is the China Xi》</a>，有推友<a href=\"https://twitter.com/InFangjay/status/1008912586216235008?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw&amp;ref_url=https%3A%2F%2Fchinadigitaltimes.net%2Fchinese%2F2018%2F06%2F%25e3%2580%2590%25e4%25bc%2597%25e4%25ba%25ba%25e6%258e%25a8%25e3%2580%2591%25e3%2580%258athis-is-the-china-xi%25e3%2580%258b%2F\">@wsg102</a> 为其添加了五字句版本的字幕。</p>\n<blockquote><p>6月23日，有推友 <a href=\"https://twitter.com/l5d/status/1011316907700572160?s=21\">@L5d</a> 提供了《Xi Jinping: Last Week Tonight with John Oliver》的中字版本，字幕来源未知（视频下载<a href=\"https://www.freeinchina.org/xi-jinping-last-week-tonight-with-john-oliver-john-oliver-hbo/\">地址</a>）。26日，有推友 <a href=\"https://twitter.com/liouderhuey/status/1011444185793118208\">@liouderhuey</a> 将中字版本上传至Vimeo。</p></blockquote>\n<p><iframe src=\"https://player.vimeo.com/video/277000992?app_id=122963\" width=\"600\" height=\"338\" frameborder=\"0\" title=\"约翰&middot;奥利弗美国脱口秀狂酸习近平（中文字幕）\" webkitallowfullscreen mozallowfullscreen allowfullscreen></iframe></p>\n<p>6月25日，多家媒体报道称John Oliver的节目在中国网络上遭到屏蔽，连带播映节目的美国电视网络HBO的网站也在中国被封锁。（BBC）</p>\n<p><strong>相关阅读：</strong></p>\n<p><a href=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2018/06/bbc-%E7%BA%A6%E7%BF%B0%C2%B7%E5%A5%A5%E5%88%A9%E4%BD%9B%E7%A2%B0%E7%BA%A2%E7%BA%BF-%E8%AE%A9%E4%B8%AD%E5%9B%BD%E7%94%9F%E6%B0%94%E7%9A%84%E6%94%BF%E6%B2%BB%E8%84%B1%E5%8F%A3%E7%A7%80/\">BBC | 约翰·奥利佛碰红线 让中国生气的政治脱口秀</a></p>\n<p><a title=\"【众人推】《This is the China Xi》\" href=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2018/06/%e3%80%90%e4%bc%97%e4%ba%ba%e6%8e%a8%e3%80%91%e3%80%8athis-is-the-china-xi%e3%80%8b/\">【众人推】《This is the China Xi》</a></p>\n<p><a title=\"德国之声︱脱口秀“吐槽”习近平 HBO官网遭封杀 2018.06.25\" href=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2018/06/%e5%be%b7%e5%9b%bd%e4%b9%8b%e5%a3%b0%ef%b8%b1%e8%84%b1%e5%8f%a3%e7%a7%80%e5%90%90%e6%a7%bd%e4%b9%a0%e8%bf%91%e5%b9%b3-hbo%e5%ae%98%e7%bd%91%e9%81%ad%e5%b0%81%e6%9d%80/\">德国之声︱脱口秀“吐槽”习近平 HBO官网遭封杀</a></p>\n<p><a title=\"【众人推】收拾不了洋人我还收拾不了你？ 2018.06.21\" href=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2018/06/%e3%80%90%e4%bc%97%e4%ba%ba%e6%8e%a8%e3%80%91%e6%94%b6%e6%8b%be%e4%b8%8d%e4%ba%86%e6%b4%8b%e4%ba%ba%e6%88%91%e8%bf%98%e6%94%b6%e6%8b%be%e4%b8%8d%e4%ba%86%e4%bd%a0%ef%bc%9f/\">【众人推】收拾不了洋人我还收拾不了你？</a></p>\n<p><strong>中国数字空间｜<a title=\"习近平个人崇拜\" href=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/space/%E4%B9%A0%E8%BF%91%E5%B9%B3%E4%B8%AA%E4%BA%BA%E5%B4%87%E6%8B%9C\">习近平个人崇拜</a></strong></p>\n","author":1015,"categories":[18271,18270,18269,13770],"tags":[34970,34969,27070,13222,29740]}